reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Pettit, Becky (March 2000). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://crcw.princeton.edu/workingpapers/WP98-04-Pettit.pdf\">\"Moving and Children's Social Connections: the critical importance of context\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <i>Center for Research on Child Wellbeing Working Papers</i>. CRCW, Princeton University<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">22 January</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Center+for+Research+on+Child+Wellbeing+Working+Papers&amp;rft.atitle=Moving+and+Children%27s+Social+Connections%3A+the+critical+importance+of+context&amp;rft.date=2000-03&amp;rft.aulast=Pettit&amp;rft.aufirst=Becky&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcrcw.princeton.edu%2Fworkingpapers%2FWP98-04-Pettit.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADisenfranchised+grief\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Iowa_State_University_paper_by_Lesia_Oesterreich-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Iowa_State_University_paper_by_Lesia_Oesterreich_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Oesterreich, Lesia (April 2004). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.extension.iastate.edu/Publications/PM1529G.pdf\">\"Understanding children: moving to a new home\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. Iowa State University<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">22 January</span> 2010</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Understanding+children%3A+moving+to+a+new+home&amp;rft.pub=Iowa+State+University&amp;rft.date=2004-04&amp;rft.aulast=Oesterreich&amp;rft.aufirst=Lesia&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.extension.iastate.edu%2FPublications%2FPM1529G.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADisenfranchised+grief\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Wertsch-p10-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Wertsch-p10_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a href=\"/wiki/Mary_Edwards_Wertsch\" title=\"Mary Edwards Wertsch\">Wertsch, Mary Edwards</a> (April 23, 1991). <i>Military Brats: Legacies of Childhood Inside the Fortress</i> (1st hardcover ed.). Harmony. p.&#160;350. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-517-58400-X\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-517-58400-X\">0-517-58400-X</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Military+Brats%3A+Legacies+of+Childhood+Inside+the+Fortress&amp;rft.pages=350&amp;rft.edition=1st+hardcover&amp;rft.pub=Harmony&amp;rft.date=1991-04-23&amp;rft.isbn=0-517-58400-X&amp;rft.aulast=Wertsch&amp;rft.aufirst=Mary+Edwards&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADisenfranchised+grief\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Journal_Article-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Journal_Article_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\">Stepp, G (2007). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vision.org/visionmedia/grief-and-loss/disenfrachised-grief/2202.aspx\">\"Disenfranchised Grief\"</a>. <i>Vision Journal</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 November</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Vision+Jou